# Architecture

**Scope:** Better Auth `auth` schema in core only — no product Prisma domains in shared dashboard `lib/`. Features = removable subtrees.

**Deps:** sub-feature → segment `lib/` → `src/lib` \| `src/components`. No cross-sibling feature imports.

**Colocate:** route tree + segment `lib/` + `src/app/action/<feature>/` (one mutation per file).

**SSOT:** `*-routes.ts`, `cache-tags.ts` per segment; UI from `src/components/ui`. Links: `render={<Link … />}`, not `asChild`.

Before new helpers: scope upward; compose shadcn first.

**Detail (Read):** [docs/agents/architecture.md](docs/agents/architecture.md). **UI:** [docs/agents/ui-design.md](docs/agents/ui-design.md).
